<!DOCTYPE html>
<html data-bs-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Worldout</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container-fluid">
      <h1>World of the left-outs</h1>
      <p>Do you time to time feel the world we're in not of your favorite taste? What's the world you'd like to be part of? Here is where we define and build the world that works best for us.</p>

      <h2>Are you interested?</h2>
      <p>We're actively looking for help in following area: 1. law maker, 2. software developer, 3. blockchain epxerts, 4. marketing 5. business operation & development. Send your resume at <a href="mailto:jobs@worldout.org">jobs@worldout.org</a></p>

      <h3>Global feeds</h3>
      <div class="mb-4">
        <a data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
          Visit cities & towns
        </a>
        <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
          <div class="">
          <% cities.forEach(c => {%>
            <a href="/cities/<%=c.city%>"><%=c.city%></a> (P<%=c.population/1000000%>, <%=c.gdp/1000000000%>)
          <% }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <% for(let i=0; i<100; i++) { %>
        <div class="card mb-1">
          <div class="card-header">
            9/2/2024 21:26 in City of <a href="/cities/Busan">Busan</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
              <p>A well-known quote, contained in a blockquote element.</p>
              <footer class="blockquote-footer">recorded by <cite title="Source Title">MayorKim</cite></footer>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div><% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script>
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
